data.description: This extraordinary residence has been meticulously refurbished, offering a remarkable abode that is sure to captivate any potential buyer. The interior boasts a tasteful blend of two-toned paint, complemented by the presence of luxurious stainless steel appliances and exquisite marble countertops. An elegant dining chandelier adorns the space, while ceiling fans and blinds provide both comfort and privacy throughout. The lower level features beautiful tile flooring, perfectly harmonizing with the elegant gray carpeting that graces the upper level. The bathrooms are adorned with high-quality fixtures and Calcutta style tile baths, exuding a sense of timeless sophistication. The yard has been designed to require minimal maintenance, both in the front and rear sections, while a covered patio offers respite from the sun's rays. Additionally, the master bedroom unveils a private balcony, providing a serene retreat. Do not miss out to showcase this exceptional property!
